%% MLServer Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.1/MLServer.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant DP as DataPlane
    participant Model as MLModel.predict()
    participant MetricsSrv as MetricsServer<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant KafkaIn as Kafka Input Topic<br/>9092/TCP
    participant KafkaSrv as MLServer KafkaServer
    participant KafkaOut as Kafka Output Topic<br/>9092/TCP
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>gRPC OTLP

    Note over Client, Gateway: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Platform auth (TLS)
    Gateway->>REST: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>No auth (in-cluster)
    REST->>DP: Route to DataPlane
    DP->>Model: predict(payload)
    Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
    DP-->>REST: JSON Response
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP 200
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client, Gateway: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: ModelInfer RPC<br/>Auth: Platform auth (TLS)
    Gateway->>GRPC: Forward (gRPC/8081)<br/>No auth (in-cluster)
    GRPC->>DP: Route to DataPlane
    DP->>Model: predict(payload)
    Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
    DP-->>GRPC: gRPC Response
    GRPC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over KafkaIn, KafkaOut: Flow 3: Kafka Async Inference (Optional)
    KafkaIn->>KafkaSrv: Consume from<br/>mlserver-input topic
    KafkaSrv->>DP: Route to DataPlane
    DP->>Model: predict(payload)
    Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
    DP-->>KafkaSrv: Result
    KafkaSrv->>KafkaOut: Produce to<br/>mlserver-output topic

    Note over Prom, MetricsSrv: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>MetricsSrv: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8082

    Note over REST, OTel: Flow 5: Tracing (Optional)
    REST-->>OTel: OTLP traces (gRPC)
    GRPC-->>OTel: OTLP traces (gRPC)
